5|$|Call of Duty 2 was {{the most}} popular launch title on the Xbox 360, with 200,000units sold in its first week of availability. 77% of people who {{purchased}} an Xbox 360 also purchased <b>the</b> <b>game,</b> which contributed to its high sales. As of July 2006, 1.4million copies of <b>the</b> <b>game</b> <b>had</b> been sold on the Xbox 360. By January 2008, <b>the</b> <b>game</b> <b>had</b> sold 2million copies. By November 2013, <b>the</b> <b>game</b> <b>had</b> sold 5.9 million copies.|$|R
